title: Ghana youth striker Benjamin Tetteh scores on Standard Liege senior debut in friendly defeat
text:
Sports News | 9 October 2015 20:25 CET Ghana youth striker Benjamin Tetteh scores on Standard Liege senior debut in friendly defeat - www.ghanasoccernet.com Benjamin Tetteh 
Ghana youth striker Benjamin Tetteh scored on his Standard Liege senior debut on Friday evening as they lost 3-2 to German Bundesliga II side Fortuna Dusseldorf. 
The lanky forward leveled the scoring for the Reds to make it 2-2 before Dusseldorf snatched the winner through Sercan Serarer.
